I paint somebody else's mural.

09:19.217 --> 09:21.584
I paint Simpson's album covers.

09:21.586 --> 09:24.620
Then when I finally quit
to freelance,

09:24.622 --> 09:26.521
not only do I almost
starve to death,

09:26.523 --> 09:27.989
