take me back?

09:49.709 --> 09:53.143
Simple. You're good, and you're
the fastest painter around.

09:53.145 --> 09:57.113
But this time no more artsy-craftsy
Sonny Malone touches, huh?

09:57.115 --> 09:59.548
Just enlarge the album cover
the way I give it to you.

09:59.550 --> 10:01.550
Am I coming in loud and clear?

10:01.552 --> 10:03.585
Yeah. Good. Here.

10:03.587 --> 10:06.867
You're on your way to your
next masterpiece. Get started.

10:10.025 --> 10:11.257
That's great, isn't it?

10:11.259 --> 10:13.659
Picasso only gets
to be called a genius.

10:13.661 --> 10:16.028
I get to be called
the fastest painter around.

10:16.030 --> 10:19.131
Hey, Sonny, I have this terrific friend.
You interested?

10:19.133 --> 10:21.967
Not right now. Hey.

10:21.969 --> 10:24.002
Mmm, she's great looking.

10:24.004 --> 10:26.671
I think that's this crazy girl
I just ran into.

10:26.673 --> 10:27.938
Yeah? I was walking
through the park.

10:27.940 --> 10:30.907
She nearly ran over me,
then she kissed me.

10:30.909 --> 10:32.942
Okay, now, let's hear
the X-rated version.

10:32.944 --> 10:35.644
What did you do?
Nothing. She took off.

10:35.646 --> 10:37.579
She took off? Come on!

10:37.581 --> 10:40.281
Is this the same Sonny Malone
that drives women crazy?

10:40.283 --> 10:42.249
I'm gonna go find out
who she is.

10:42.251 --> 10:44.635
You mean right now?

10:44.636 --> 10:47.020
Hey, you're definitely gonna be a
successful artist, Malone. You know why?

10:47.022 --> 10:50.256
- Because you're nuts!
- Simpson's gonna kill him.

10:50.258 --> 10:53.325
Listen, Sonny, I told you.
I don't know who she is.

10:53.327 --> 10:56.594
She never filed a W-2
and she never got a check.

10:56.596 --> 10:59.163
And if I never paid her,
she just doesn't exist.

10:59.165 --> 11:00.864
What do you mean,
she doesn't exist?

11:00.866 --> 11:02.966
I'm looking right at her. She's
on the Nine Sisters album.

11:02.968 --> 11:05.268
Not if I didn't pay her,
she isn't!

11:05.270 --> 11:07.837
- Down here at me.
- Now look to your right.

11:07.839 --> 11:09.839
Yeah, that's good.

11:09.841 --> 11:11.273
Listen, Sonny,
I don't know who she is.

11:11.275 --> 11:14.943
How can you not know who she is?
You took the picture.

11:14.945 --> 11:20.381
Listen, this sounds strange, but there
wasn't supposed to be a model on this cover.

11:20.383 --> 11:22.616
I snapped maybe 100 shots.

11:22.618 --> 11:25.251
In one of them, this girl
just jumped into frame.

11:25.253 --> 11:28.120
The next time I saw her
was on the contact sheets.

11:28.122 --> 11:30.722
I liked it, so I used it.
That's the whole story.

11:30.724 --> 11:31.989
She just appeared?

11:31.991 --> 11:35.176
No, no, appeared
then disappeared.

11:35.177 --> 11:38.362
Now, don't you go spreading this around.
This is one of my best covers.

11:38.364 --> 11:40.230
Why do you want to know
who she is, anyway?

11:40.232 --> 11:41.897
I like her.

11:45.302 --> 11:48.202
Hey, Lou. You seen
her around here?

11:48.204 --> 11:52.806
No. Pretty. Hey, you're single, right?
Let me show you my daughters.

11:52.808 --> 11:56.142
That's great, Lou. I'm gonna go
look where I saw her this morning.

11:56.144 --> 11:57.705
Come on, get your balloons.

11:59.079 --> 12:01.145
Seventy-five cents.

12:02.715 --> 12:05.015
- I'll meet you later.
- All right.

12:05.017 --> 12:06.249
