at AirFlo Records.

13:12.372 --> 13:14.038
You in the music business?

13:14.040 --> 13:16.740
What are you? Are you a record producer?
A sound engineer?

13:16.742 --> 13:19.042
No. I'm sort of a painter.

13:19.044 --> 13:22.078
You, you paint
at a record business?

13:22.080 --> 13:26.182
Well, not exactly paint. What I
do is, I duplicate record covers.

13:26.184 --> 13:28.718
But why?

13:28.719 --> 13:31.253
I make album covers bigger so you can
hang them outside record stores.

13:31.255 --> 13:33.989
Promotion. Sounds like
an interesting job, huh?

13:33.991 --> 13:36.491
Yeah. Sounds like you should
take real long lunch hours.

13:36.493 --> 13:37.925
You got it.

13:37.927 --> 13:39.293
You know, I used to be
in the music business,

13:39.295 --> 13:41.962
but now I'm
what you might call retired.

13:41.964 --> 13:44.097
It's a refined name for "bum."

13:46.501 --> 13:48.434
I don't believe it.

13:48.436 --> 13:51.003
Hey! Hey, wait a minute!

13:51.005 --> 13:53.271
Hey, kid. Hey, wait up!
Where are you going?

13:53.273 --> 13:55.806
Hey, you! Come on! Hold on!

13:58.076 --> 14:00.109
Oh, hi. Listen, I gotta borrow this.
I'll bring it back.

14:00.111 --> 14:01.877
Sure. If you bring
it back in person.

14:01.879 --> 14:03.211
You got it.

14:17.191 --> 14:18.123
Hey!

14:23.296 --> 14:26.263
Hey, wait a minute!
Where are you going?

14:36.241 --> 14:38.274
Get that bike off the pier!

14:45.515 --> 14:47.381
Oh, shit!

14:57.492 --> 14:59.391
Whoo!

14:59.393 --> 15:01.926
You're a real Errol Flynn, kid.

15:01.928 --> 15:04.395
What other stunts do you do?

15:04.397 --> 15:06.029
Man, this whole thing
is screwing me up.

15:06.031 --> 15:07.231
What whole thing? Ah, nothing.

15:07.232 --> 15:09.365
Come on, have a cup of coffee.

15:11.635 --> 15:15.503
Sometimes the best person to
tell something to is a stranger.

15:15.505 --> 15:17.972
Go on. What's on your mind?

15:17.974 --> 15:19.173
Okay.

15:20.342 --> 15:22.141
I run into this girl
this morning.

15:22.143 --> 15:23.542
Never saw her before
in my life.

15:23.544 --> 15:25.911
She kisses me and disappears.

15:25.913 --> 15:28.079
So what's so weird about that?

15:28.081 --> 15:30.598
What's so weird about that is

15:30.599 --> 15:33.116
that 10 minutes later I see her picture
on an album cover I'm supposed to paint.

15:33.119 --> 15:35.986
I mean, that's crazy, right?

15:35.988 --> 15:39.923
Well, if I said it sounded crazy,
would you stop looking for her?

15:39.925 --> 15:41.925
No. Then why ask?

15:43.028 --> 15:45.194
So I'll keep looking for her.

15:46.197 --> 15:48.478
Okay, kid, but take
a tip from me.

15:49.466 --> 15:51.532
What's that?

15:51.534 --> 15:53.667
Don't look underwater anymore.

15:55.637 --> 15:57.336
Thanks a lot.

16:02.008 --> 16:03.340
Hey, Al, where you going?

16:03.342 --> 16:05.709
Hey, Sonny.
It's good to see you, man.

16:05.711 --> 16:08.045
How you doing, Big Al?

16:08.046 --> 16:10.380
How could I go wrong with the great
paint job you did on my van?

16:10.382 --> 16:12.081
Hey, and the chicks love it.

16:12.083 --> 16:14.316
Yeah. It's one of the
finer examples of my work.

16:14.318 --> 16:16.184
It's beautiful, man.
Where you headed?

16:16.186 --> 16:17.451
East. Where you going? West.

16:17.453 --> 16:19.519
Hang on. I'll give you a ride.
No, that's cool.

16:19.521 --> 16:23.022
Forget it. I owe you one.
All right. Okay, hit it.

16:25.659 --> 16:29.394
Relax and enjoy it, man.
We're taking the scenic route.

16:29.396 --> 16:32.230
Yeah, just don't forget
I'm back here.

16:37.370 --> 16:39.336
Hey, that's the place
on the album cover!

16:39.338 --> 16:40.603
Slow down, I wanna
get off here.

16:40.605 --> 16:43.272
Here? Thanks for the ride.

16:43.274 --> 16:45.307
Anytime, Sonny.

17:36.458 --> 17:40.493
<i>I've always been in your mind.</i>

17:42.163 --> 17:45.130
<i>You know I will be kind.</i>

17:45.132 --> 17:48.500
<i>I'll be guiding you.</i>

17:48.502 --> 17:51.769
<i>Building your dream.</i>

17:51.771 --> 17:54.638
<i>Has to start now.</i>

17:54.640 --> 17:58.541
<i>There's no other road to take.</i>

18:00.344 --> 18:03.244
<i>You won't make a mistake.</i>

18:03.246 --> 18:07.514
<i>I'll be guiding you.</i>

18:09.050 --> 18:11.150
Wow.

18:11.152 --> 18:15.587
<i>We have to believe</i>
<i>we are magic.</i>

18:15.589 --> 18:20.391
<i>Nothing can stand in our way.</i>

18:20.393 --> 18:25.062
<i>You have to believe</i>
<i>we are magic.</i>

18:25.064 --> 18:29.399
<i>Don't let your aim ever stray.</i>

18:29.401 --> 18:34.102
<i>And if all your hopes survive.</i>

18:34.104 --> 18:38.105
