Me.

19:04.126 --> 19:07.460
Hey, I've been asking
about you all day.

19:07.462 --> 19:10.296
You may not believe this, but I'm
painting an album cover and you're on it.

19:10.298 --> 19:12.398
Why shouldn't I believe it?

19:12.400 --> 19:14.867
Because before today,
I never laid eyes on you.

19:14.869 --> 19:17.236
Now I've seen you three times
in one day.

19:17.238 --> 19:19.438
That's a little
too coincidental.

19:19.440 --> 19:21.840
Sounds like
you don't believe it.

19:21.842 --> 19:23.508
Well, with all
that's happened to me today,

19:23.510 --> 19:25.877
to tell you the truth,
I don't believe it.

19:25.879 --> 19:29.881
You're right. It's too coincidental.
Someone must be setting us up.

19:29.883 --> 19:32.116
What do you mean?
Hey, wait a minute!

19:32.118 --> 19:33.617
I didn't have anything
to do with this!

19:33.619 --> 19:34.884
Really?

19:34.886 --> 19:36.852
Yeah, really, I didn't.

19:37.387 --> 19:38.753
Hey!

19:43.526 --> 19:45.859
Who said I was talking
about you?

19:47.195 --> 19:49.461
You come here often?

19:49.463 --> 19:52.564
Yes. I can practice my skating
and no one bothers me.

19:53.500 --> 19:55.366
You must live around here then.

19:55.368 --> 19:57.634
Sometimes.

19:57.636 --> 20:01.270
Say, you think we could...
See each other again?

20:01.272 --> 20:02.871
Yeah. Would you like that?

20:02.873 --> 20:04.372
Why?

20:04.374 --> 20:06.540
I don't know. I don't have
a very good reason.

20:06.542 --> 20:08.783
I'd just like to see you again.

20:09.845 --> 20:11.444
Where are you?

20:13.414 --> 20:14.780
I don't know where
I'm supposed to look.

20:14.782 --> 20:18.316
<i>Bring all your dreams alive.</i>

20:19.752 --> 20:21.184
<i>For you.</i>

20:24.189 --> 20:26.488
We'll see each other again.
Bye, Sonny.

20:29.192 --> 20:30.791
How'd you know my name?

20:33.829 --> 20:36.229
Hey, wait a minute!
I don't know your name.

20:36.231 --> 20:37.596
<i>Kira.</i>

20:40.334 --> 20:41.533
Kira.

20:49.642 --> 20:51.241
I was in big trouble.

20:51.243 --> 20:52.275
So what did you do about it?

20:52.277 --> 20:54.443
Nothing. Hi, Sonny.

20:54.445 --> 20:55.777
What are you doing here?
It's early.

20:55.779 --> 20:57.378
Yeah, it's really early.

20:57.380 --> 20:58.912
I'm working.

20:58.914 --> 21:00.480
Well, that's wonderful.

21:00.482 --> 21:02.782
Oh, hello there.

21:02.784 --> 21:05.184
Why, do you know
you bear a strong resemblance

21:05.186 --> 21:06.685
to a fellow by the name
of Sonny?

21:06.687 --> 21:08.420
Oh, yeah. He works here.

21:08.422 --> 21:13.191
Always comes in late, though.
Say, that's pretty damn good.

21:13.193 --> 21:17.595
It is. It's too good.
That's what's wrong with it.

21:17.597 --> 21:21.231
It is supposed to look exactly
like the album cover I gave you.

21:21.233 --> 21:22.899
Is that too difficult?

21:22.901 --> 21:25.434
If you want me to work,
I'll work.

21:25.436 --> 21:28.270
If you want to stand there and
argue, I can get into that, too.

21:28.272 --> 21:31.573
Don't be a wise ass, Malone.
That painting should be done.

21:31.575 --> 21:33.708
What are you wasting
all this time on the girl for?

21:33.710 --> 21:35.910
Because that's how
she really looks.

21:35.912 --> 21:40.547
I don't give a damn how she really looks.
Just get it finished.

21:40.549 --> 21:42.215
Now, when are you gonna
have it done?

21:42.217 --> 21:44.750
Well, I'd say it probably
will be done

21:46.687 --> 21:48.620
when it's done.

21:48.622 --> 21:50.822
But that's only
an approximate guess.

21:52.826 --> 21:56.427
Five minutes, my office.
If it's six, keep walking.

22:00.266 --> 22:01.932
Sonny, what did you do?

22:04.369 --> 22:07.336
Nobody likes it, but we all
say yes and then forget it.

22:07.338 --> 22:10.238
It goes with the job.
Four minutes.

22:10.240 --> 22:11.572
What difference does it make?

22:11.574 --> 22:13.440
I'll say it's Tuesday,
he'll say it's Wednesday.

22:13.442 --> 22:15.909
So, big deal. Tell him it's Wednesday.
What does it cost?

22:15.911 --> 22:19.279
Oh, nothing.
Maybe just the truth.

22:19.281 --> 22:21.681
Just go in there and agree with him.
That's all he wants.

22:21.683 --> 22:23.482
You want me to say that
Tuesday's Wednesday, right?

22:23.484 --> 22:24.716
Everyday of the week.

22:24.718 --> 22:26.884
Three and a half minutes.

22:26.886 --> 22:28.352
All right!

22:30.289 --> 22:31.954
I'll be right back.

22:34.458 --> 22:35.658
