not the way you want to do them.

23:12.421 --> 23:15.722
But sometimes I see more in these
covers than what's really there.

23:15.724 --> 23:18.024
That's art.

23:18.026 --> 23:20.493
Just paint what
you're told to paint.

23:20.495 --> 23:22.828
