butt over to the Platinum Palace.

23:40.409 --> 23:42.041
Tuesday's Wednesday.

24:05.733 --> 24:07.999
Hey, clarinet. How you doing?

24:08.001 --> 24:10.768
Hey, what do you say, kid.
What're you doing up there?

24:10.770 --> 24:12.035
Trying to get down.
Grab a hold of the ladder.

24:12.037 --> 24:14.070
Sure.

24:14.072 --> 24:16.772
Hey, if we keep meeting like this, we
might as well introduce ourselves.

24:16.774 --> 24:19.007
Sonny Malone. Danny McGuire.

24:19.009 --> 24:21.943
Malone and McGuire.
Sounds like a vaudeville team.

24:21.945 --> 24:23.678
What you got there?
Oh, this is a real gem.

24:23.680 --> 24:24.979
I've been waiting
months for it.

24:24.981 --> 24:26.547
Ah, Glenn Miller.

24:26.549 --> 24:28.949
You wouldn't know about him.
He was before your time.

24:28.951 --> 24:31.484
So was Beethoven,
but I know who he is.

24:31.486 --> 24:32.952
Do you like Glenn Miller?

24:32.954 --> 24:35.054
Do you like rock and roll?
I love rock and roll.

24:35.056 --> 24:36.455
I love Glenn Miller.

24:43.896 --> 24:45.662
This place is incredible.

24:45.664 --> 24:47.797
It belonged to a silent
movie star.

24:47.799 --> 24:51.500
Obviously, they did things
big in those days.

24:51.502 --> 24:53.101
What do you do
with all this space?

24:53.103 --> 24:55.453
Nothing really.

24:55.454 --> 24:57.804
But I love this room because it
makes my records sound great.

24:57.807 --> 25:00.174
Well, I've only got
one thing to say.

25:00.176 --> 25:01.975
Remember, I gave you
some popcorn.

25:01.977 --> 25:05.745
Okay. But you came here
to listen to Glenn Miller.

25:05.747 --> 25:09.148
So, all set up. There he goes.

25:09.150 --> 25:13.485
Nothing like that sound, huh?
That sound was a miracle.

25:13.487 --> 25:14.519
Hey, Danny, that's you.

25:14.521 --> 25:15.820
Yeah.

25:17.123 --> 25:20.057
Hey, this girl...
Danny, there's this girl...

25:20.659 --> 25:21.991
Listen.

25:24.695 --> 25:26.027
That's me.

25:26.029 --> 25:28.896
Hey, that's all right.
You got anymore surprises?

25:30.933 --> 25:33.900
This is what I call
my memorabilia room.

25:33.902 --> 25:36.702
Sort of the story
of Danny McGuire.

25:36.704 --> 25:39.071
Tommy Dorsey, Benny Goodman.
You really knew those guys?

25:39.073 --> 25:41.573
Yeah. We used to all
hang out together.

25:41.575 --> 25:43.875
